{
  "id": "adv_bond_kkr_01_05",
  "title": "赤崎こころ5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁあぁぁぁぁん、髪がうまくまとまらないっ！\nもう一回やり直しじゃぁぁぁっ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaaah‚ my hair just won't stay put!\nI have to start all over again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "（くるくるっとお団子を二つ作って……）\n（うん、位置と大きさはいい感じ。でも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Twirl it up into two buns…）\n（Hmm‚ the position and size are good. But…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "（昨夜凄く疲れてて髪を乾かさずに寝落ちしちゃったから）\n（髪がゴワゴワ……にしてもゴワゴワし過ぎじゃ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I fell asleep without drying my hair last night because I was so tired‚）\n（so my hair is so frizzy… wait‚ isn't it TOO frizzy!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "（くんくん……うわ……最悪だ……最悪だよ……）\n（これ、シャンプーとボディーソープ間違えてる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sniff‚ sniff… Wow… this is the worst…）\n（I used body soap instead of shampoo by mistake.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "（どれだけヘアアイロンで丁寧に伸ばしても）\n（サラサラにならない訳だ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（No matter how carefully I use the hair iron‚）\n（it’s not getting silky at all…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0830155055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.4496821721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "（わわ……今鏡見て気付いたけど後ろもヤバい！）\n（変な寝ぐせが付いてぴょんってなってる！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait… I just saw in the mirror‚ the back is a mess too!）\n（It’s got a weird bedhead sticking out!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4496821721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 49.8496821721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "（愛ちゃんに後ろだけアイロンしてもらいたいけど）\n（今日は日直だからって早めに寮を出て行った気が……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I want Ai-chan to iron the back for me‚ but）\n（I think she left early for her school duties…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8496821721,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7083.651161199995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.4496821721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、こころちゃーん。怜ちゃんもすずちゃんも\nもう寮出たけど平気？　そろそろ出ないと遅刻じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kokoro-chan. Rei-chan and Suzu-chan\nalready left the dorm‚ are you okay? You’ll be late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4496821721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.920021693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん！　全然平気じゃないです～\nちょっと、こころのお部屋に入ってきてくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan! I am NOT okay at all~\nCould you come into my room for a second?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.920021693,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7250.311215700009
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7646.644973600004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.1703329087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　あと十分くらいで出ないと\n学校遅刻しちゃうよ。強風で電車も遅延してるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened? If you don't leave within ten minutes‚\nyou’ll be late for school. Even the trains are delayed by high winds…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.986681239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.8395227752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことよりも大変！　大変なんです！\nこころの髪がゴワゴワでぴょんってなってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not the problem! This is a DISASTER!\nMy hair is all frizzy and sticking out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8395227752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.0061894419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにいつもよりちょっと髪の調子が\n良くなさそうだけど、そんな気にするほどでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It does look a little less\nmanageable than usual‚ but it’s not that bad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0061894419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.1757361415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "こころは気になるんです！　後ろのぴょんってなってる\nとこ、ちょっとこのアイロンで伸ばしてくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I care! This part sticking out in the back‚\ncould you please iron it out for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1757361415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.2090694748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かった！　いくよ、スーッと……\nはい、これで真っすぐになったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay! Here we go‚ sliding it down…\nThere‚ now it’s nice and straight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2090694748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.6784118337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます～！　これでようやく外に出――\nああぁっ！　今度は前髪が気になり始めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you~! Finally‚ I can go outsi――\nAaah! Now I’m starting to worry about my bangs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6784118337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.5784118337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "もうちょっとだけ内側に巻いて、斜めに流して……\n左右のバランスが悪いな……右の触角を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Curl it inward just a bit more‚ and sweep it to the side…\nThe balance is off… the hair on the right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.211745167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.4450744314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、私もそろそろ学校行くね\n遅刻したらまた莉央さんに怒られちゃうよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro-chan‚ I have to get going to school too.\nYou’ll get in trouble with Rio-san again if you’re late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4450744314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.1502844813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ～！　遅刻はしません！\n裏技で学校行くんで、あと五分はのんびり出来ます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine~! I won’t be late!\nI have a secret trick to get to school‚ so I can relax for 5 more minutes~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1502844813,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11816.377099199997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7883.048852000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.7836178146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "裏技……？　あ、琴乃ちゃん、芽衣ちゃん待って～！\nじゃあね、こころちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A secret trick…? Oh‚ Kotono-chan‚ Mei-chan‚ wait for me~!\nSee you later‚ Kokoro-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7836178146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.5999949138
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.5735740028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
